---
title: Porcini Mushroom Spaghetti Bolognese with Rocket & Pear Salad
description: Vegetarians can still get a rich, hearty and satisfying bowl of pasta with this bolognese based on two types of delicious mushrooms. Cook up the chunky, veggie-packed sauce then toss it through perfectly al dente pasta for an Italian feast that will make you cry "Bravo!"

*Each week, we search the country to source the best ingredients, with a focus on quality and variety. This week's basil was in short supply, so we've replaced it with oregano. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
